Carrefour Says Knight Vinke Questioned Dia Spinoff

-- B y   A n d r e w   R o b e r t s
-- 
2011-04-14T17:27:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/carrefour-says-knight-vinke-questioned-dia-spinoff-correct-.html
(Corrects typographical error in headline.)  Carrefour SA (CA)  shareholder Knight
Vinke Asset Management LLC has questioned the company’s plans to
spin off its Dia discount chain and 25 percent of its real-
estate unit, Chief Financial Officer Pierre Bouchut said on a
conference call. Bouchut said he hasn’t met representatives of
Knight Vinke, which owns more than 1 percent of the retailer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Roberts in Paris at 
 aroberts36@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Jarvis at 
